  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://f1.ct.hjfile.cn/pic/201402/d76483b9-133c-4537-b7cd-fd4ae258f2c9.jpg\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>沪江名师Erin：纵横职场英语系列（二）<br />\n\t\t</strong>时间：4月9日（星期三） 19:30 - 20:30<br />\n\t\t主讲老师：Erin（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/erin/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a>）<br />\n\t\t公开课地点：英语活动室（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>讲师简介：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>想加入Erin老师CT粉丝团吗？快来回帖！<a href=\"http://s.hujiang.com/topic/119034/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">戳我 &gt;&gt;&gt;</a></strong></span></p>\n\t<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" height=\"247\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\" width=\"578\">\n\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201404/47976fc30d75417182eae27b118b7693.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></td>\n\t\t\t\t<td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serief; line-height: 22px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Erin，大葱老师</strong></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serief; line-height: 22px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">沪江网校英语名师。商务英语、口语、写作授课经验丰富，美语发音地道，语言教学细腻不浮夸。授课中，尤其关注语言应用背景，思维方式和文化内涵。希望通过这些信息的引入，让学习者更全面理解语言沟通，&ldquo;感性&rdquo;地说出一口好英语。主讲网校《剑桥国际英语》系列，《实战商务口语》，《中考英语写作高效提分》等课程，深受学员喜爱。</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/erin/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;</a></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t</tbody>\n\t</table>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>课堂内容提要：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><span style=\"color: #000;\">Hosting a Dinner Party</span></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>1.Warm up</strong><br />\n\t\t-Dinner party etiquette is not really about knowing every detail of which fork to use. True etiquette is more than knowing what the &quot;rules&quot; are. As all the etiquette books stress, the heart of true etiquette is making other people comfortable.<br />\n\t\t-If you are the host or hostess, it&rsquo;s good if you know the rules. You would never correct your guests, but sometimes they might be watching you to get an idea of dinner party etiquette. If you are a guest, you will feel more comfortable if you can maneuver your way smoothly through the manners minefield.</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>2.Business Talk</strong><br />\n\t\t-making people feel welcome and comfortable<br />\n\t\t-showing interest in others<br />\n\t\t-refusing offers politely</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>3.Takeaways</strong><br />\n\t\tA: Alright, everyone, dinner is ready. Would you like to take a seat?<br />\n\t\tC: Great! Can I sit here?<br />\n\t\tB: Sure. Sit wherever you like. We are not set in our ways or anything. Please go ahead and start. Make yourself right at home.<br />\n\t\tD: Wow, amazing spread. I can't wait to dig in.</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>4.Top Tip</strong><br />\n\t\t-Express and address dietary needs.<br />\n\t\t-Bring a gift for your host<br />\n\t\t-Pace yourself.<br />\n\t\t-Express your appreciation.</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>5.show interests in someone's home:</strong><br />\n\t\t-Your floors are beautiful, are they oak?<br />\n\t\t-I really like what you've done with the deco. It's both homy and chic at the same time.<br />\n\t\t-Are you the original owners?<br />\n\t\t-Looks like you've redone your kitchen, looks great!</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">想获取本次公开课的讲义：<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/9359138/diary/420180/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;&gt;点击查看&lt;&lt;</a></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></strong></span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/app/event\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>最新活动预约</strong></a></span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"